* {{ill|lt=Ōkuninushi|Q276944|qid=Q276944|lt=Ōkuninushi-no-Mikoto|1=Ōkuninushi}}

=== Cultural properties ===
'''Yaizu City designated tangible cultural property'''
* Jōyatō stone lantern: Bunsei 5 (1822)

=== Sessha and massha ===
The following three shrines stand in the precincts.

'''Precinct shrines'''
* Tsushima Shrine - Deity: {{ill|Susanoo-no-Mikoto|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|qid=Q272993|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}}
* Aoki Shrine - Deity: Sudō Samon
* Inari Shrine - Deities: {{ill|lt=Toyouke-hime|Q2983724|qid=Q2983724|lt=Toyouke no Kami|1=Toyouke-hime}}, Miketsu-no-kami, {{ill|qid=Q3080728|lt=Ukanomitama|Q3080728|qid=Q3080728|lt=Uka-no-Mitama-no-Kami|1=Ukanomitama}}

